{"tid":2385894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"{全城中伏}掛住GME但我地唔撚記得咗呢樣野","createTime":"2021-01-29T09:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T13:01:32.000Z","uid":525,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"742b7d894833196f34ee714883e42f55ce215e0f","tid":2385894,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:13:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>就係Be humble阿</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個星期因為GME大家嘈到拆天<br />\n咩難聽說話同私怨mode都倒哂出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持走嘅下下誅心屌人為錢賣港<br />\n仲講到話要美國制裁埋入臨立會嘅人<br />\n<br />\n而支持留嘅又瘋狂屈人係鬼係藍屍<br />\n<br />\n趁大家嘈到面紅耳熱分哂陣營咁<br />\n不如樓豬同大家回顧下另一d野?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">方仲賢因為laser pen俾狗咬<br />\n當晚太空館即興集會聲援</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oR9f5F2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoR9f5F2.png&h=4ee7323c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong><span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">衝衝子同牧師都可以攬埋一齊<br />\n杯葛定留任又有幾大件事?</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g6hpY05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg6hpY05.png&h=10ced391&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>醫護教師公務員航空業廣告界..<br />\n全港各行各業集會we connect</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zg9ge0S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzg9ge0S.png&h=51c27df3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>為咗救被困機場嘅手足<br />\n全民出車變港版鄧蔻克</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NDQ7ck7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDQ7ck7.png&h=12545718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>十萬人冒槍炮反包營救理大<br />\n和理非集體變勇武執磚傘陣火魔</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1xPG1ev.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1xPG1ev.png&h=c6ff5577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>就兩個星期前,蘋果被皇軍佔領<br />\n爆賣報紙,狂落廣告,股票抗爭都玩埋</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/59XNcmc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F59XNcmc.png&h=f06b111b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>你捨得將呢一年嘅團結破壞嗎?</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔想就留下口唔好對自己人鬧到咁盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n運動本身就係充滿分歧<br />\n和定勇,陣地定游擊,港島定開花<br />\n舉唔舉美國旗,去唔去加泰集會...<br />\n大家為唔同議題嘈過無數次<br />\n<br />\n但點解過咗一年幾依然團結?<br />\n因為點屌都好,大家都唔會當對方係敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可以覺得手足廢,豬隊友,左膠,衝動撚...<br />\n但唔該記住<span class=\"red\"><strong>敵人只有一個-共產黨及其爪牙</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a698c47b94fee1d0415dfef9733e8541c470081","tid":2385894,"uid":245201,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:14:09.000Z","msg":"唔記得左屌你老母個臭系。"},{"pid":"708d72c48656f767b9ebf83b7e3429591f945e4a","tid":2385894,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:18:07.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"1be76c9faa5e8b8c65f01e5f0aa5e89b7f4caa33","tid":2385894,"uid":331551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8ec4190af6e5e8bc1f78650cf0631528c20548","tid":2385894,"uid":389613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:20:00.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">我可以幫你擋子彈，你可以陪我攬炒中共嗎？<br />\n香港人用 BNO 係搬石頭砸中共春袋</span><br />\n<br />\n原來用 BNO 離開係 Trump 一早 set 左比中共既計時炸彈！我地更應該繼承 Trump 既精神，用 BNO 逼 Biden 同中共開戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">只要有大批香港人離開，會造成現時已經虛弱既經濟徹底崩潰，而中共強行鎖國則引來百國聯軍。</span><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本１：支共反制 BNO 會引致戰爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[武俠小說] 因為 BNO 香港變成外交博奕戰場！Trump 偷偷地幫香港插左支定海神針迫 Biden 打柒中共！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2377934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2377934</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２：支共比 BNO 走引致經濟崩潰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[神話故事] 中共經濟末日狂奔，BNO 就係大衛與歌利亞決戰粒石頭。港人出走成就 Trump 滅共偉業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2380593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380593</a><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n不論你係撐 Trump 既手足、定係支持滅共既手足，今次 BNO Visa 係時候身體力行，用你對腳投票去支持 Trump 呢條滅共戰線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"red\"> 多你一個好多，少你一個唔掂！你既決定將會成為世界走向正義定係腐敗既關鍵因素！</span>"},{"pid":"b69625597b236e0ca567ca7ea64e9751c8d47bb2","tid":2385894,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:23:50.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"20e7aa769749dba063226864b6d0f3e690b11b8b","tid":2385894,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b69625597b236e0ca567ca7ea64e9751c8d47bb2","tid":2385894,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:23:50.000Z","msg":"雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b314c43e717be43b6a3d45cdce972325a602c1","tid":2385894,"uid":79562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w78XXsq.gif